### Test Top Stations By Revenue API

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7095/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. GET Top 10 Stations - Default (Current Month)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 2. GET Top 5 Stations - Current Month
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations?topCount=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. GET Top 3 Stations - By Month (October 2024)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations/by-month?month=10&year=2024&topCount=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. GET Top 10 Stations - By Quarter (Q4 2024)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations/by-quarter?quarter=4&year=2024&topCount=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 5. GET Top 5 Stations - By Custom Date Range
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations/by-custom-date?startDate=2024-10-01&endDate=2024-10-31&topCount=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. GET All Stations (Top 50) - Using Query Params
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations?Month=11&Year=2024&topCount=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

