### ============================================
### Error Cases
### ============================================

### Invalid topCount (0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations?topCount=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 400 Bad Request

### Invalid topCount (> 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations?topCount=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 400 Bad Request

### Invalid Month
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations/by-month?month=13&year=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 400 Bad Request

### Invalid Quarter
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations/by-quarter?quarter=5&year=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 400 Bad Request

### No Authentication
GET {{baseUrl}}/Dashboard/top-stations
### Expected: 401 Unauthorized
